
// This Hyperlambda snippet updates the value of the [.total-score] node by adding the value of [.base-score] and a static integer 10. The [set-value] slot assigns the result of the [math.add] operation, which sums the current value of [.base-score] and 10, to [.total-score].
set-value:x:@.total-score
   math.add
      get-value:x:@.base-score
      .:int:10
